summary: Dedicated, hardworking and proactive Electrical Engineer with 3 years of working experience and a strong background in solar energy. Always enthusiastic to learn and undertake new challenges and develop new skills. Quick self-learner and highly adaptable to all challenging situations. Developed good planning & organisational skills and can confidently work independently or as part of a team. Able to work well under pressure and adhere to strict deadlines. Motivated to explore career potentials.
